uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon_util

Class KKeyedList<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon_util.KList<V>
      • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon_util.KKeyedList<K,V>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FIdentifiables

    public abstract class KKeyedList<K,V>
extends KList<V>
    Abstract class whose extensions represent ordered lists, with element value-types that enable each value to be mapped to an associated "key" object, and where the key object can be retrieved via the value object itself.

    See KList for details of additional list-operations and associated listening mechanisms.
